        <item>
            <title>Apple 回应 Mac mini 电源键设计  「用户几乎无需手动开关机」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/10/mac-mini-power-design/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mac-mini-power-design</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/10/mac-mini-power-design/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 09:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274198</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 最新推出 Mac mini 因其独特的电源键设计引发用家回响。Mac mini 将电源键安置于机身底部，根据 Apple 高管的解释，这一设计并非偶然，而是经过多方考量，以配合 Mac mini 的缩小尺寸和不同于传统电脑的操作方式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/macminipowerbutton.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/macminipowerbutton-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/macminipowerbutton-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/macminipowerbutton.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/macminipowerbutton-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aba86eafc66f0491.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aba86eafc66f0491-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aba86eafc66f0491-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/aba86eafc66f0491.jpg 1268w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Apple 副总裁 Joz 和 John 在近日接受访问时表示，2024 款 Mac mini 的体积仅为前代的一半，使其需要更精巧的设计方案，将电源键放置于底部成为合适选择。同时，Apple 进一步强调，Mac mini 的待机设计意味著用户几乎不会频繁使用电源键，装置长时间运行不会产生过多噪音或耗电问题，与 Windows 装置存在显著差异。</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: #262626;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">Mac </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">运行</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">机制更像智能电话、平板电脑，是一台随时待机的设备，待机期间并不会带来太高耗电量、噪音等困扰。</span>而且系统不会因为长时间开机导致资源占用过多，随时都是良好状态，不用通过重启进行系统清理。</p><p><span style="font-kerning: none;"></span></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1453830.htm">cnBeta</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
