        <item>
            <title>郑州学生集体夜骑引发交通堵塞，美团：频繁长途骑行可能影响身体健康</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/10/zhzh-night-rides/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zhzh-night-rides</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/10/zhzh-night-rides/life-tech/sport-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 08:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运动科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[共享单车]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[美团]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274193</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 18.7px 0.0px; font: 18.7px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">近日郑州大学生夜间骑行至开封引起极大热潮，众多学生甚至吸引到外地人参加，导致当地交通压力显著增大。这场夜骑活动在共享单车的广泛使用下，带来严重的交通堵塞，甚至多部门紧急出动设立临时护栏，以减少对车流的影响。针对此情况，滴滴青桔与美团单车分别发布倡议书，呼吁大学生理性使用共享单车，考虑出行安全与骑行健康问题。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ee97b26a3725f68.jpeg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ee97b26a3725f68-357x580.jpeg" alt="" width="357" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ee97b26a3725f68-357x580.jpeg 357w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ee97b26a3725f68.jpeg 554w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 357px" /></a></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">滴滴青桔指出，长途夜间骑行存在安全隐患，尤其是在繁忙道路上行驶时，事故风险更高。夜晚视线不佳，加上骑行距离过长，容易因疲劳引发事故，严重威胁骑行者安全。</span>美团方面也强调，频繁的长途骑行可能对身体健康产生不良影响，特别是对于平日缺乏锻炼的大学生而言，长时间的骑行易导致肌肉拉伤及其他健康问题。此外，长途骑行引致的单车磨损率高，为维修工作带来额外压力，也不利于其他用户的正常租用体验。美团呼吁大学生尽量选择火车、长途汽车等公共交通工具，以确保出行的安全与便利。</p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">法国媒体《RFI》分析指，规模一度超过「</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">白纸运动」</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">时的群众集会。</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">11 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">月 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">8 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">日晚间，有超过 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">20 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">万人加入骑行队伍，整个骑行队伍绵延数十公里，场面震撼。此次活动虽未带有政治抗议色彩，但河南多所大学紧急宣布封校，防范类似群体行为扩大，并呼吁学生减少夜间出行。相关事件迅速在中国社交媒体上掀起热议，「</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">夜骑开封被按下暂停键」</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">等话题一度登上热搜榜首。</span></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">据消息，大批学生包揽共享单车，自郑州沿郑开大道骑行至开封，全程 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">50 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">公里。夜间骑行的庞大队伍甚至引来警察关注，然因规模巨大，执法人员未敢阻拦。媒体报道称，这是继上周末的首次大规模夜骑活动后，学生再度组织万人骑行，吸引邻近省市学生参与其中。虽然参与者未表达政治诉求，部分人手持国旗并唱起中国国歌，获得开封市民的欢迎，形成一种看似爱国的社会活动。</span></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">随著夜骑事件影响扩大，开封市区多处因共享单车摆放而堵塞，市政府不得不进行清理。</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">11</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">月</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">9</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">日下午，郑州与开封的交警部门联合发布通知，决定自当日下午</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">4</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">时至次日中午，对郑开大道的非机动车道进行临时禁行，以确保道路通行。</span></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">这次夜骑开封的活动走红始于 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">2024 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">年 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">6 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">月，当时 </span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none;">4 </span><span style="font-kerning: none;">名女大学生为品尝开封灌汤包，从郑州骑行至开封，并将这段旅程的经历发布在短影片平台，引发众多仿效者。随后，夜骑活动逐渐演变成一种流行文化，吸引大量学生参与，甚至成为当地推广夜间旅游的契机。开封市政府一度宣布夜间景区对学生免费开放，市长吴海燕还曾表示将优化夜游路线，迎接大客流，确保游客安全。</span></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Songti TC'; color: #262626;"><span style="font-kerning: none;">然而，随著夜骑规模的爆发式增长，政府开始加强控制，尤其是在看到数十万学生聚集的情景后，更显谨慎。从过往的「</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">白纸运动」</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">到这次的大规模夜骑，这些群体性活动令当局警觉。河南省教育厅会议指示，各高校应对此类活动保持警惕，防止有反社会人士或境外敌对势力借机煽动。多所高校随即封校，并警告学生不得再参与夜骑活动。网上甚至流出校方威胁学生的信息，声称事件已上升至「</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">政治事件」</span><span style="font-kerning: none;">，参与者将面临严重后果。</span></p><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px Georgia; color: #262626; min-height: 19.0px;"><p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 16.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px Georgia; color: #420178;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Songti TC'; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #262626;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1453838.htm"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Georgia; font-size-adjust: none; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #420178;">cnBeta</span></a>、<a href="https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/%E8%A6%81%E9%97%BB%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/20241109-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%99%BD%E7%BA%B8%E8%83%9C%E4%BC%BC%E7%99%BD%E7%BA%B8-%E9%83%91%E5%B7%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%9C%E9%AA%91%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2">Rfi</a></span></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
