        <item>
            <title>中国 Audi 弃用「四环」标志，与上汽合作电动车只用「AUDI」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/09/audi-e-concept/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=audi-e-concept</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/09/audi-e-concept/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 14:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[audi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273934</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>之前曾经有传闻指 Audi 将会在与中国上汽合作推出的电动车系列上使用新的品牌标记，最近终于在上海车展曝光，在原型车上不再见到经典的「四环」标志，改为「AUDI」字样。<br /><span id="more-1273934"></span></p><p>今次展示的 E concept 是 Audi 与上汽合作开发的电动车，采用全新数码化平台，搭载 800 伏特架构，本身开发代号为「Purple」，正式亮相后也不再使用品牌惯用的「E-Tron」命名。而最受到关注的就是车头和车尾都不见 Audi 本身的标志，只是用了「AUDI」字样代替。基于这个原型车开发的车款将会是为中国市场而设的特别型号，因此其他现有 Audi 车款暂时不会转用新标志。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244567_largejpg-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273935" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244567_largejpg-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244567_largejpg.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244563_largejpg-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273936" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244563_largejpg-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244563_largejpg.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Audi 总裁 Gernot Döllner 在新闻稿中表示，此举是为了吸引中国市场更注重科技的消费者，这些消费者「期待领先的连接性和自动驾驶技术」。据路透社报导，面对中国本地品牌的激烈竞争，Audi 在 2024 年上半年于中国市场的销量不足 1 万部，促使品牌重新定位。不过本身辨识度极高的「四环」标志改为「AUDI」后，所带来的会是正面作用还是反效果，则仍然有待观察。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244557_web_1920-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273939" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244557_web_1920-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244557_web_1920.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244558_web_1920-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273940" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244558_web_1920-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/a244558_web_1920.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.audi-mediacenter.com/en/press-releases/double-debut-in-shanghai-audi-and-the-audi-e-concept-16359">Audi</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
